patthana14.19:1.1_0: Saññojanaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nosaññojano dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe…

patthana14.19:2.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava.
